title: Side by Side Duplex, Large Kitchen, Private Decks, 3 Levels
posting_body: ['3 Level Side by Side Duplex in Merriam Park Available', 'Now, Large Kitchen, Back Deck, In Unit Laundry, Garage Stall', 'Property Address', '1669-1671 Hague Ave. - 1671 | St. Paul, MN 55104', 'Available: Now', 'Offered By', 'Guardian Property Management |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'To apply, go to <URL>  Each adult would apply at <URL> and upload last two pay statements and proof of other income.', 'Side by side duplex in Merriam Park available now.', ' Hardwood floors on the main level.', ' Large kitchen with all appliances including a dishwasher and microwave.', " There's a 3/4 bathroom on the main floor with tiled shower.", 'There are three bedrooms upstairs along with a full bathroom.', ' The 4th bedroom is the entire 3rd level - open lofted area with a large closet.', 'The basement is unfinished.', " There's a washer/dryer and plenty of extra room for storage.", ' This unit has a small private deck in the front and back of the property.', " There's one garage stall included in rent.", ' Great Merriam Park location one block off Selby and two blocks off Snelling.', ' Walking distance to Whole Foods and tons of shops and restaurants.', 'We would also do a shorter term lease through 5/31/23.', 'Rent includes trash service.', 'Up to two cats or small dogs (under 40 lbs) are okay with a $50/month pet fee per', '$50 application fee per adult', 'We check income (gross household income must be at least 3 times rent), credit (must be 600+), criminal and rental history', 'Call Dakota at', 'show contact info', 'to schedule a showing.', 'Agent: Dakota DeHaven', 'BROKER: GUARDIAN PROPERTY MANAGEMENT AND SERVICES LLC', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 4BD/2.0BA', 'Square Feet: 1,600', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $2,200.00', 'Available: Now', 'Application Fee: $50.00', 'Security Deposit: $2,200.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Small dogs allowed']
